Class ArchiveParse

java.lang.Object
com.laoluade.ingestor.ao3.repositories.ArchiveParse
@Entity public class ArchiveParse extends Object

This class defines the JPA entity for an archive server parse.

    • ArchiveParse

      public ArchiveParse(ArchiveParseType parseType, String parseTargetLink, int parseChaptersCompleted, int parseChaptersTotal, String parseResult)

      This constructor creates the parse entry in the ArchiveParse JPA table.

      Parameters:
      parseType - The kind of parse the parse entry is.
      parseTargetLink - The web link the parse is targeting.
      parseChaptersCompleted - How many chapters the parse has finished analyzing.
      parseChaptersTotal - The total number of chapters the parse needs to analyze.
